Package static_comp

Class Grid

  • java.lang.Object
    • static_comp.Grid

  • public class Grid
extends java.lang.Object
    Grid is a Class that holds the fields needed by the whole Simulation Their fields are set based on the XML file and they will not be changed during the simulation

      • Grid

        public Grid​(int n,
            int m,
            java.util.ArrayList<Point> obts,
            java.util.ArrayList<Edge> sZones,
            Point initial_pos,
            Point final_pos)
        Constructs Grid Edges according to its size and inserts special zones, obstacles and final/initial point
        Parameters:
        n - width of the grid
        m - height of the grid
        obts - array list of Point that are obstacles
        sZones - array list of Edge are zones with a special cost
        initial_pos - initial position where the initial individuals are set
        final_pos - final position where the individuals want to reach
